description:
AJCR-03 EMBROIDERED NET 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Shirt: Net Trouser: Twisted Silk Dupatta: Net Color: Purple

Swathed in the mystique of twilight, this dress is a purple dream woven into existence. Champagne gold zari, like sunbeams kissing a lavender sky, are studded with stardust-like sequins. Threads in mauve and deep purple hues dance in harmony, creating a masterpiece of color. The embroidered dupatta, a wispy cloud of enchantment, finishes this ensemble with the grace of a fairytale ending.
DESIGN DETAILS:

Embroidered front & back bodice with bodice hem on net
24 embroidered kalis for peshwas on net
5 meter embroidered border for hemline of peshwas on net
Pair of embroidered sleeves with border on net
2.5 meter embroidered dupatta on net with 4 side borders
1.5 meter wide width twisted silk for trouser
